생성 및 텍스트 그리기\n        Using font As New Font(fontFamily, fontSize, FontStyle.Bold)\n            Dim sf As New StringFormat()\n            sf.Alignment = StringAlignment.Center\n            sf.LineAlignment = StringAlignment.Center\n\n            Dim textColor As Color = If(e.CellStyle.ForeColor = Color.Empty, Color.Black, e.CellStyle.ForeColor)\n            Using brush As New SolidBrush(textColor)\n                e.Graphics.DrawString(cellValue, font, brush, textRect, sf)\n            End Using\n        End Using\n\n        e.Handled = True\n    Catch\n        ' CellPainting 예외 시 기본 렌더링으로 처리\n    End Try\nEnd Sub\n```\n\n### 알고리즘 설명\n- **이진 탐색(Binary Search)**을 사용하여 최적 폰트 크기 계산\n- 최소 크기 16, 최대 크기 40 범위에서 `MeasureString`으로 텍스트 크기를 측정\n- 셀 범위(패딩 제외)에 맞는 최대 폰트 크기를 반환\n- DataGridView의 CellPainting 이벤트에서 실시간으로 각 셀마다 적용"}],"stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":2,"cache_creation_input_tokens":478,"cache_read_input_tokens":23588,"output_tokens":1013,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":478},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}},"requestId":"req_011CYzG39NPU8bjpSSGWimCX","type":"assistant","uuid":"d86e6c17-c504-4fc9-b375-e212c3c636fe","timestamp":"2026-03-13T02:05:21.749Z","userType":"external","cwd":"C:\\Users\\Administrator\\Desktop","sessionId":"a8e0b76c-4368-49d5-9d2c-48543228912d","version":"2.1.74","gitBranch":"HEAD","slug":"polymorphic-bouncing-beacon"}
